<H2>Install Openbravo ERP on Debian Linux</H2></tr>

<tr><td><table border=0 width=100% cellpadding=0 cellspacing=9><tr><td width=10% valign=center align=center><font size=2 color=#333333><a href=/voteup/?inode=11867><img src=up.gif border=0 alt="Up"></a><br>vote<br><a href=/votedown/?inode=11867><img src=down.gif border=0 alt="Down"></a></font></td><td width=1 bgcolor=#bbbbbb><br></td>
<td width=90% valign=top></b>
